# Trivy CVE allowlist for the three ghcr.io/i40sys images (decision-021,
# task-067.10). One CVE id per line to accept an un-actionable / un-fixable
# finding; document WHY next to each. Empty by default — the build-image.yml
# Trivy step (severity HIGH,CRITICAL, ignore-unfixed) honours this file.
#
# Example:
#   CVE-2024-12345  # base image, no upstream fix; not reachable in our usage
